canonical:
  title: 神勒寺
  author: 李達善
  language: lzh
  text: 禪房僧已寂獨坐夜將分知有漁舟過江心人語聞
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 神勒寺
  author: 李達善
  language: lzh
  text: 禪房僧已寂。獨坐夜將分。知有漁舟過。江心人語聞。
korean:
  title: 신륵사
  author: 이달선
  language: kor
  text: |-
    선방의 스님들 고요해졌는데
    혼자 앉았으매 밤중이 지내려 한다
    고기잡이 배가 지나감을 알 수 있다니
    강 복판에서 사람의 말소리가 들린다
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_1450_010_0110&viewSync=OT
  footnotes: []
english:
  title: Sinryeuk Temple
  author: Lee Dal-seon
  language: eng
  text: |-
    The meditation hall grows still—the monks at rest.
    I sit alone as night draws near its end.
    A fishing boat passes on the river;
    From the water's heart, human voices drift to shore.
  footnotes:
    - Sinryeuk Temple (神勒寺) is a historical Buddhist temple located on an island in the Yeongsan River in Korea, known for its serene setting and spiritual atmosphere.
